{"id":232353900,"title":"一個月薪資多少才有一般的生活品質？","content":"最近在臉書看到一個日本服飾公司的徵才廣告，文案大概就是月薪¥200000起跳，然後配上附圖(已將公司名稱和露臉廣告人物碼掉，若有不妥會移除)\nhttps://i.imgur.com/DU2QTu7.jpg\n下面不外乎就是一堆日本拿60K根本也沒賺多少的留言\n20萬日幣再扣稅、健保和房租那些等等，也真的賺不了多少😓\n\n在日本工作的各位覺得一個月薪資大概多少才能維持一定的生活品質呢？就是沒有說要賺很多但至少不會為了平衡，要常吃泡麵、麵包或為錢所困的狀況；又或者說是多少的月薪才有待在日本工作比台灣好的認知呢？(單薪資方面不探討環境或其他因素)","excerpt":"最近在臉書看到一個日本服飾公司的徵才廣告，文案大概就是月薪¥200000起跳，然後配上附圖（已將公司名稱和露臉廣告人物碼掉，若有不妥會移除），下面不外乎就是一堆日本拿60K根本也沒賺多少的留言，20萬","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ee51d6cd-ad7e-4d73-b79a-3ce32ea7798b","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-22T18:40:58.543Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-22T18:45:43.927Z","commentCount":20,"likeCount":51,"tags":[],"topics":["日本工作","日本生活","日本打工度假"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"日本生活","forumAlias":"japan_life","school":"靜宜大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":51}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/DU2QTu7.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"b025e4d9-21ca-45aa-afdf-adcd2321e823","url":"https://i.imgur.com/DU2QTu7l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/DU2QTu7l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/DU2QTu7l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-22T18:40:58.543Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-22T18:45:43.927Z"},{"id":"b025e4d9-21ca-45aa-afdf-adcd2321e823","url":"https://i.imgur.com/DU2QTu7.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/DU2QTu7","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/DU2QTu7l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-22T18:40:58.543Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-22T18:45:43.927Z"}],"postAvatar":""}